data.title: Biographies and Charts
data.text: Listed below by Surname are the names and links each Tinneny descendant whose biography has been posted. All of the biographies can be traced back to one of the ancestors listed in the above chart. With each person's number is a letter identifying from which of Thomas1's children each person is descended. To request a specific Tinneny descendant's biography be placed on the priority posting list click this link Request a Biography. Please be sure to clearly describe the person whose biography you are requesting since there are many descendants with the same names.
